        "name": "Keen Smell",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Your nose becomes more sensitive to the scents of the wild, the better for you to track your quarry. For the spell\u2019s duration, you gain scent as an imprecise sense with a range of 30 feet. Your hunted prey can\u2019t be undetected by you as long as it\u2019s within your scent range.",
